==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tiddledywinks
<hw>Tid"dle*dy*winks`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A game in
which the object is to snap small disks of plastic, bone, ivory, or the
like, from a flat surface, as of a table, into a small cup or basket; --
called also <altname>tiddlywinks</altname>.</def> <mark>[U.
S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

